lead_paragraph: Australia's stand-in skipper David Warner led by example, hitting a brilliant century in their five-wicket win against Sri Lanka to complete a 4-1 series victory on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Warner Ton Secures Australia's Win in Final ODI
